    {
      "text": "A 67-year-old man is admitted with pneumonia requiring mechanical ventilation. He has a history of congestive heart failure and diabetes mellitus. During his stay, he becomes profoundly hypotensive and requires intravenous vasopressors for several hours. His blood pressure stabilizes, and ventilation settings are weaned over the next day. There is no known history of excessive acetaminophen use, recent travel, or new medication administration (see lab results).\n\n\nTest\nResult\nNormal Values\n\n\n\nAspartate aminotransferase\n2450 IU/L\n12 - 40 IU/L\n\n\nAlanine aminotransferase\n2100 IU/L\n5 - 40 IU/L\n\n\nTotal bilirubin\n34 μmol/L\n3.5 - 16.5 μmol/L\n\n\nAlkaline phosphatase\n110 IU/L\n39 - 117 IU/L\n\n\n\nWhich of the following best explains the cause of this patient’s elevated hepatic enzymes?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Intrahepatic cholestasis related to antibiotic therapy"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Transient low blood flow to the liver causing hepatocellular necrosis"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Toxic liver injury from analgesic overuse"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "text": "Immune-mediated hepatic inflammation triggered by infection"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 2,
      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\">Antibiotic</a>-induced <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j60_kS&anker=Zd0ed3eb208321943f24b364e0a464294\" data-learningcard-id=\"j60_kS\" data-anker=\"Zd0ed3eb208321943f24b364e0a464294\">liver</a> injury usually presents with a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=uF0pP3&anker=Z6e7c956eb18ad0e0bd932d39b2781881\" data-learningcard-id=\"uF0pP3\" data-anker=\"Z6e7c956eb18ad0e0bd932d39b2781881\" data-section-id=\"cvWa_M0\" data-sememe-id=\"17d2kr0\">cholestatic pattern</a>, with elevated <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z78c098e284dee4ae95afddad9ababaa4\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z78c098e284dee4ae95afddad9ababaa4\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"rmYfSp\">alkaline phosphatase</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z07a8a4f4a850245bf742b6a98121b3e0\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z07a8a4f4a850245bf742b6a98121b3e0\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"HmYKSp\">bilirubin</a>. The patient's dramatic <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Zde6636a7a9eaab224426560b3e3b2b4c\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Zde6636a7a9eaab224426560b3e3b2b4c\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"MmYMTp\">transaminase</a> elevations and hypotensive episode indicate hepatocellular injury due to <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=VP0GdT&anker=Zbc05e544d46e794a60ac9ce9ec6883af\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-anker=\"Zbc05e544d46e794a60ac9ce9ec6883af\" data-section-id=\"k9cmne0\" data-sememe-id=\"WQ0PEf\">ischemia</a>, not <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=jS0_z2&anker=Z3811ba77a88bcd2cc789df34c5379055\" data-learningcard-id=\"jS0_z2\" data-anker=\"Z3811ba77a88bcd2cc789df34c5379055\" data-section-id=\"EXW8-P0\" data-sememe-id=\"Vu0GJ3\">cholestasis</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) CORRECT:</h4>The patient's profound <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rM0fJg&anker=Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-learningcard-id=\"rM0fJg\" data-anker=\"Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-section-id=\"oVc0vY0\" data-sememe-id=\"nGb7-E\">hypotension</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=kO0msT&anker=Z75813684cbaddcd436339b6b8d787255\" data-learningcard-id=\"kO0msT\" data-anker=\"Z75813684cbaddcd436339b6b8d787255\" data-section-id=\"ZI1ZYR0\" data-sememe-id=\"qNbCX8\">vasopressor</a> use led to decreased hepatic <span data-sememe-id=\"Ef18LT0\">perfusion</span>, causing <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hs0Kwh&anker=Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hs0Kwh\" data-anker=\"Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-sememe-id=\"xicEFX0\">ischemic hepatitis</a>. This condition results in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=VP0GdT&anker=Z28b2cd3d009fe208ee54280c99b41b38\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-anker=\"Z28b2cd3d009fe208ee54280c99b41b38\" data-section-id=\"R9clMe0\" data-sememe-id=\"O8aI5m\">necrosis</a> of centrilobular <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j60_kS&anker=Z817900248cb9da0368affabc6607850d\" data-learningcard-id=\"j60_kS\" data-anker=\"Z817900248cb9da0368affabc6607850d\" data-section-id=\"WvcP_V0\" data-sememe-id=\"ejXxzB\">hepatocytes</a>, which are most sensitive to <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ZI0ZYh&anker=Z10519b65a196f32c0f4399dded5949dd\" data-learningcard-id=\"ZI0ZYh\" data-anker=\"Z10519b65a196f32c0f4399dded5949dd\" data-section-id=\"5h1ieg0\">oxygen deprivation</a>. The marked elevation in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z1e451667f863dcfa4a71041436f9de6f\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z1e451667f863dcfa4a71041436f9de6f\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"LmYwTp\">aspartate aminotransferase</a> (<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z1e451667f863dcfa4a71041436f9de6f\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z1e451667f863dcfa4a71041436f9de6f\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"LmYwTp\">AST</a>) and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z0153ae0f06ed75e2633214306264cc89\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z0153ae0f06ed75e2633214306264cc89\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"nmY7Tp\">alanine aminotransferase</a> (<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z0153ae0f06ed75e2633214306264cc89\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z0153ae0f06ed75e2633214306264cc89\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"nmY7Tp\">ALT</a>) levels, often exceeding 1000 IU/L, reflects acute hepatocellular injury. This pattern, in the context of <span data-sememe-id=\"3LdSxq0\">hemodynamic instability</span>, is characteristic of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hs0Kwh&anker=Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hs0Kwh\" data-anker=\"Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-sememe-id=\"xicEFX0\">ischemic hepatitis</a>.<br><br><span class=\"wichtig\"><b>Key learning point: </b></span><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hs0Kwh&anker=Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hs0Kwh\" data-anker=\"Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-sememe-id=\"xicEFX0\">Ischemic hepatitis</a>, or <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hs0Kwh&anker=Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hs0Kwh\" data-anker=\"Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-sememe-id=\"xicEFX0\">shock liver</a>, is characterized by a sudden increase in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j60_kS&anker=Zd0ed3eb208321943f24b364e0a464294\" data-learningcard-id=\"j60_kS\" data-anker=\"Zd0ed3eb208321943f24b364e0a464294\">liver</a> enzymes following a hypotensive episode, often seen in critically ill patients.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=oF00Q3&anker=Z58fbab9a84c7c9ef0b226ec58881e66a\" data-learningcard-id=\"oF00Q3\" data-anker=\"Z58fbab9a84c7c9ef0b226ec58881e66a\" data-sememe-id=\"HbbKEH\">Acetaminophen toxicity</a> can cause <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=uF0pP3&anker=Z2f43b8b9dc95cdb5bd93da3c354a3916\" data-learningcard-id=\"uF0pP3\" data-anker=\"Z2f43b8b9dc95cdb5bd93da3c354a3916\" data-sememe-id=\"GlXByy\">elevated transaminases</a>, but the stem excludes excessive <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=BN0zWg&anker=Za3da7a7c0e6eb1d1d781615b1c2c7af3\" data-learningcard-id=\"BN0zWg\" data-anker=\"Za3da7a7c0e6eb1d1d781615b1c2c7af3\" data-section-id=\"Ykcnmc0\" data-sememe-id=\"gvYFzI\">acetaminophen</a> use. The patient's <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rM0fJg&anker=Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-learningcard-id=\"rM0fJg\" data-anker=\"Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-section-id=\"oVc0vY0\" data-sememe-id=\"nGb7-E\">hypotension</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=kO0msT&anker=Z75813684cbaddcd436339b6b8d787255\" data-learningcard-id=\"kO0msT\" data-anker=\"Z75813684cbaddcd436339b6b8d787255\" data-section-id=\"ZI1ZYR0\" data-sememe-id=\"qNbCX8\">vasopressor</a> use suggest <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hs0Kwh&anker=Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hs0Kwh\" data-anker=\"Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-sememe-id=\"xicEFX0\">ischemic hepatitis</a>, characterized by high <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Zde6636a7a9eaab224426560b3e3b2b4c\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Zde6636a7a9eaab224426560b3e3b2b4c\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"MmYMTp\">transaminase</a> levels and reduced hepatic <span data-sememe-id=\"Ef18LT0\">perfusion</span>, rather than toxic injury.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) INCORRECT:</h4>Immune-mediated <span data-sememe-id=\"VpcGoW0\">hepatitis</span> typically presents with a gradual increase in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j60_kS&anker=Zd0ed3eb208321943f24b364e0a464294\" data-learningcard-id=\"j60_kS\" data-anker=\"Zd0ed3eb208321943f24b364e0a464294\">liver</a> enzymes and is associated with chronic or subacute inflammation. The patient's acute hypotensive episode and extremely high <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Zde6636a7a9eaab224426560b3e3b2b4c\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Zde6636a7a9eaab224426560b3e3b2b4c\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"MmYMTp\">transaminase</a> levels suggest <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=VP0GdT&anker=Zbc05e544d46e794a60ac9ce9ec6883af\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-anker=\"Zbc05e544d46e794a60ac9ce9ec6883af\" data-section-id=\"k9cmne0\" data-sememe-id=\"WQ0PEf\">ischemic</a> injury rather than an immune-mediated process.</div>",
