    {
      "text": "An 82-year-old man is hospitalized for pneumonia. He has a longstanding history of congestive heart failure. Over the past 24 hours, he has become increasingly hypotensive, with blood pressures as low as 80/50 mm Hg, and has produced minimal urine. On examination, he appears lethargic with cool extremities but no jugular venous distension. He has no known history of chronic liver disease (see lab results and report).\n\nBlood pressure\n80/50 mm Hg\n\n\n\nTest\nResult\nNormal Values\n\n\n\nAspartate aminotransferase\n1785 IU/L\n12 - 40 IU/L\n\n\nAlanine aminotransferase\n1610 IU/L\n5 - 40 IU/L\n\n\nAlkaline phosphatase\n220 IU/L\n39 - 117 IU/L\n\n\nTotal bilirubin\n23 μmol/L\n3.5 - 16.5 μmol/L\n\n\n\nAbdominal ultrasound: No biliary ductal dilation or gallstones\nWhich of the following is the most likely cause of his acute hepatic injury?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Acute viral hepatitis"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Acetaminophen toxicity"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Biliary obstruction in the common duct"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "text": "Hypoperfusion-mediated hepatic necrosis"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 4,
      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<span data-sememe-id=\"p-YLy7\">Acute viral hepatitis</span> can cause significant <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Zde6636a7a9eaab224426560b3e3b2b4c\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Zde6636a7a9eaab224426560b3e3b2b4c\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"MmYMTp\">transaminase</a> elevations, but it is usually accompanied by <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ps0LDh&anker=Zbc0d0ff153bc5c7a27589815d0c842fd\" data-learningcard-id=\"ps0LDh\" data-anker=\"Zbc0d0ff153bc5c7a27589815d0c842fd\" data-section-id=\"FfWgLk0\" data-sememe-id=\"b31HSg0\">risk factors</a> such as recent travel, exposure to contaminated food or water, or bloodborne transmission. The patient's <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rM0fJg&anker=Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-learningcard-id=\"rM0fJg\" data-anker=\"Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-section-id=\"oVc0vY0\" data-sememe-id=\"nGb7-E\">hypotension</a> and signs of poor <span data-sememe-id=\"Ef18LT0\">perfusion</span> are more indicative of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hs0Kwh&anker=Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hs0Kwh\" data-anker=\"Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-sememe-id=\"xicEFX0\">ischemic liver injury</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=oF00Q3&anker=Z58fbab9a84c7c9ef0b226ec58881e66a\" data-learningcard-id=\"oF00Q3\" data-anker=\"Z58fbab9a84c7c9ef0b226ec58881e66a\" data-sememe-id=\"HbbKEH\">Acetaminophen toxicity</a> typically presents with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=uF0pP3&anker=Z2f43b8b9dc95cdb5bd93da3c354a3916\" data-learningcard-id=\"uF0pP3\" data-anker=\"Z2f43b8b9dc95cdb5bd93da3c354a3916\" data-sememe-id=\"GlXByy\">elevated transaminases</a>, often with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z0153ae0f06ed75e2633214306264cc89\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z0153ae0f06ed75e2633214306264cc89\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"nmY7Tp\">ALT</a> levels higher than <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z1e451667f863dcfa4a71041436f9de6f\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z1e451667f863dcfa4a71041436f9de6f\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"LmYwTp\">AST</a>, following an overdose. The absence of a history of excessive <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=BN0zWg&anker=Za3da7a7c0e6eb1d1d781615b1c2c7af3\" data-learningcard-id=\"BN0zWg\" data-anker=\"Za3da7a7c0e6eb1d1d781615b1c2c7af3\" data-section-id=\"Ykcnmc0\" data-sememe-id=\"gvYFzI\">acetaminophen</a> use and the presence of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rM0fJg&anker=Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-learningcard-id=\"rM0fJg\" data-anker=\"Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-section-id=\"oVc0vY0\" data-sememe-id=\"nGb7-E\">hypotension</a> and poor <span data-sememe-id=\"Ef18LT0\">perfusion</span> suggest <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hs0Kwh&anker=Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hs0Kwh\" data-anker=\"Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-sememe-id=\"xicEFX0\">ischemic liver injury</a> rather than <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=oF00Q3&anker=Z58fbab9a84c7c9ef0b226ec58881e66a\" data-learningcard-id=\"oF00Q3\" data-anker=\"Z58fbab9a84c7c9ef0b226ec58881e66a\" data-sememe-id=\"HbbKEH\">acetaminophen toxicity</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<span data-sememe-id=\"quWCHM0\">Biliary obstruction</span> typically results in a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=uF0pP3&anker=Z6e7c956eb18ad0e0bd932d39b2781881\" data-learningcard-id=\"uF0pP3\" data-anker=\"Z6e7c956eb18ad0e0bd932d39b2781881\" data-section-id=\"cvWa_M0\" data-sememe-id=\"17d2kr0\">cholestatic pattern</a> with elevated <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z78c098e284dee4ae95afddad9ababaa4\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z78c098e284dee4ae95afddad9ababaa4\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"rmYfSp\">alkaline phosphatase</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z07a8a4f4a850245bf742b6a98121b3e0\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z07a8a4f4a850245bf742b6a98121b3e0\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"HmYKSp\">bilirubin</a>. The <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=4n03tg&anker=Z4254d71ea91bb85a18eeeaaf5e7adbef\" data-learningcard-id=\"4n03tg\" data-anker=\"Z4254d71ea91bb85a18eeeaaf5e7adbef\" data-sememe-id=\"fK0kfS\">ultrasound</a> shows no biliary ductal dilation or <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Q60ukS&anker=Z24c1b4e4cd23b046bd3ef10a99007d74\" data-learningcard-id=\"Q60ukS\" data-anker=\"Z24c1b4e4cd23b046bd3ef10a99007d74\" data-section-id=\"2FcThV0\" data-sememe-id=\"RV1l8f0\">gallstones</a>, and the clinical presentation of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rM0fJg&anker=Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-learningcard-id=\"rM0fJg\" data-anker=\"Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-section-id=\"oVc0vY0\" data-sememe-id=\"nGb7-E\">hypotension</a> and poor <span data-sememe-id=\"Ef18LT0\">perfusion</span> suggests <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hs0Kwh&anker=Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hs0Kwh\" data-anker=\"Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-sememe-id=\"xicEFX0\">ischemic liver injury</a> rather than <span data-sememe-id=\"quWCHM0\">biliary obstruction</span>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) CORRECT:</h4>\n<span data-sememe-id=\"krWmh50\">Hypoperfusion</span>-mediated hepatic <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=VP0GdT&anker=Z28b2cd3d009fe208ee54280c99b41b38\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-anker=\"Z28b2cd3d009fe208ee54280c99b41b38\" data-section-id=\"R9clMe0\" data-sememe-id=\"O8aI5m\">necrosis</a>, also known as <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hs0Kwh&anker=Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hs0Kwh\" data-anker=\"Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-sememe-id=\"xicEFX0\">ischemic hepatitis</a> or <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hs0Kwh&anker=Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hs0Kwh\" data-anker=\"Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-sememe-id=\"xicEFX0\">shock liver</a>, occurs when severe <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rM0fJg&anker=Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-learningcard-id=\"rM0fJg\" data-anker=\"Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-section-id=\"oVc0vY0\" data-sememe-id=\"nGb7-E\">hypotension</a> leads to reduced hepatic blood flow. This results in centrilobular (zone 3) <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j60_kS&anker=Z817900248cb9da0368affabc6607850d\" data-learningcard-id=\"j60_kS\" data-anker=\"Z817900248cb9da0368affabc6607850d\" data-section-id=\"WvcP_V0\" data-sememe-id=\"ejXxzB\">hepatocyte</a> <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=VP0GdT&anker=Z28b2cd3d009fe208ee54280c99b41b38\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-anker=\"Z28b2cd3d009fe208ee54280c99b41b38\" data-section-id=\"R9clMe0\" data-sememe-id=\"O8aI5m\">necrosis</a>. The patient's marked <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Zde6636a7a9eaab224426560b3e3b2b4c\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Zde6636a7a9eaab224426560b3e3b2b4c\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"MmYMTp\">transaminase</a> elevations, with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z1e451667f863dcfa4a71041436f9de6f\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z1e451667f863dcfa4a71041436f9de6f\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"LmYwTp\">AST</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z0153ae0f06ed75e2633214306264cc89\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z0153ae0f06ed75e2633214306264cc89\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"nmY7Tp\">ALT</a> levels in the thousands, and modest increases in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z78c098e284dee4ae95afddad9ababaa4\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z78c098e284dee4ae95afddad9ababaa4\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"rmYfSp\">alkaline phosphatase</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z07a8a4f4a850245bf742b6a98121b3e0\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z07a8a4f4a850245bf742b6a98121b3e0\" data-section-id=\"9acN5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"HmYKSp\">bilirubin</a>, are characteristic of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hs0Kwh&anker=Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hs0Kwh\" data-anker=\"Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-sememe-id=\"xicEFX0\">ischemic liver injury</a>. The clinical context of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rM0fJg&anker=Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-learningcard-id=\"rM0fJg\" data-anker=\"Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-section-id=\"oVc0vY0\" data-sememe-id=\"nGb7-E\">hypotension</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=br0Hfh&anker=Z77c4f329d4e1028bea9901be93bbe0ca\" data-learningcard-id=\"br0Hfh\" data-anker=\"Z77c4f329d4e1028bea9901be93bbe0ca\" data-section-id=\"QN1uah0\" data-sememe-id=\"Wb1Ps20\">lethargy</a>, cool extremities, and a history of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rS0faf&anker=Zfdf718ee7030d25f9dfb6b6603941bd5\" data-learningcard-id=\"rS0faf\" data-anker=\"Zfdf718ee7030d25f9dfb6b6603941bd5\" data-section-id=\"Slcywc0\" data-sememe-id=\"pwdLPH0\">congestive heart failure</a> further supports a diagnosis of <span data-sememe-id=\"krWmh50\">hypoperfusion</span>-mediated hepatic <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=VP0GdT&anker=Z28b2cd3d009fe208ee54280c99b41b38\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-anker=\"Z28b2cd3d009fe208ee54280c99b41b38\" data-section-id=\"R9clMe0\" data-sememe-id=\"O8aI5m\">necrosis</a>.<br><br><span class=\"wichtig\"><b>Key learning point: </b></span><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hs0Kwh&anker=Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hs0Kwh\" data-anker=\"Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-sememe-id=\"xicEFX0\">Ischemic hepatitis</a>, or <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Hs0Kwh&anker=Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Hs0Kwh\" data-anker=\"Ze7fe67322a963d88bccd5cb39faeaec7\" data-sememe-id=\"xicEFX0\">shock liver</a>, is characterized by a sudden reduction in blood flow to the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j60_kS&anker=Zd0ed3eb208321943f24b364e0a464294\" data-learningcard-id=\"j60_kS\" data-anker=\"Zd0ed3eb208321943f24b364e0a464294\">liver</a>, often associated with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rM0fJg&anker=Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-learningcard-id=\"rM0fJg\" data-anker=\"Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-section-id=\"oVc0vY0\" data-sememe-id=\"nGb7-E\">hypotension</a> or <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=kO0msT&anker=Z6023d435aa502ba29fe59ecc0f2f9df5\" data-learningcard-id=\"kO0msT\" data-anker=\"Z6023d435aa502ba29fe59ecc0f2f9df5\" data-sememe-id=\"-VbDCs\">shock</a>, leading to <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=uF0pP3&anker=Z2f43b8b9dc95cdb5bd93da3c354a3916\" data-learningcard-id=\"uF0pP3\" data-anker=\"Z2f43b8b9dc95cdb5bd93da3c354a3916\" data-sememe-id=\"GlXByy\">elevated liver enzymes</a>.</div>",
